- Modify: `packages/pipeline-worker/src/elicitation-rewrite.ts:95-101` (pass `internalPredictionText` + `failureModeSeverity` into `logInternalPrediction`)
- Modify: the `logInternalPrediction` helper definition (wherever it lives — grep in Step 1)
- Modify: the severity source — in this flow, severity comes from `intent_classification` or from the failure-mode detector upstream. Thread severity through `rewriteElicitation`'s call chain if not already present.
